command_group: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project

commands.name: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project create
commands.summary: Create a monitored Azure DevOps project resource.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project create --name
                                                                    --org-name
                                                                    --project-name
                                                                    --resource-group
                                                                    [--actionable-remediation]
                                                                    [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project list
commands.summary: List Azure DevOps projects onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project list --name
                                                                  --org-name
                                                                  --resource-group
                                                                  [--max-items]
                                                                  [--next-token]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project show
commands.summary: Get a monitored Azure DevOps project resource.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project show [--ids]
                                                                  [--name]
                                                                  [--org-name]
                                                                  [--project-name]
                                                                  [--resource-group]
                                                                  [--subscription]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project update
commands.summary: Update a monitored Azure DevOps project resource.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project update [--actionable-remediation]
                                                                    [--ids]
                                                                    [--name]
                                                                    [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                                    [--org-name]
                                                                    [--project-name]
                                                                    [--resource-group]
                                                                    [--subscription]
examples: az security security-connectors devops azuredevopsorgs projects repos update --security-connector-name myConnectorName --resource-group myResourceGroup --org-name myOrganization --project-name myProject --actionable-remediation state=Disabled

az security security-connectors devops azuredevopsorgs projects repos update --security-connector-name myConnectorName --resource-group myResourceGroup --org-name myOrganization --project-name myProject --actionable-remediation state=Enabled category-configurations[0].category=IaC category-configurations[0].minimum-severity-level=Low

commands.name: az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition is met.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops azuredevopsorg project wait [--created]
                                                                  [--custom]
                                                                  [--deleted]
                                                                  [--exists]
                                                                  [--ids]
                                                                  [--interval]
                                                                  [--name]
                                                                  [--org-name]
                                                                  [--project-name]
                                                                  [--resource-group]
                                                                  [--subscription]
                                                                  [--timeout]
                                                                  [--updated]
